177 A.3d 125 NASRIEN AWADALLAH, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. BAHA AWADALLAH, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-432 September Term 2017

079090 December 13, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002381-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
